  "architecture_summary": "VGGT is a large feed-forward transformer with minimal 3D inductive biases that predicts camera parameters, depth maps, point maps, and 3D point tracks from one, a few, or hundreds of input views in a single forward pass. It uses DINOv2 tokenization, alternating frame-wise and global self-attention, a camera head, a DPT-based dense prediction head, and a CoTracker2-based tracking module.",
